Products














World Leader in Aircraft Lighting & Simulation Systems



Since 1963, Control Products Corporation has been a pioneer in aerospace lighting industry providing interior and exterior lighting solutions for fixed-wing and rotary aircraft globally.
Control Products is the company that designed the US Air Force F-16 NVIS lighting modification kit and built the first 206F-16 NVIS  modification kits for the Air National Guard and Reserve and has been selected by the USAF for all remaining F-16s NVIS retrofits.  In addition, CPC has modified the F16 for six European Air Forces as well as the Singapore and SE Asia Air Force. CPC manufactures a wide range of products including illuminated information panels or light plates, full simulation systems for fixed wing, rotary or ground training vehicle such as the common driver trainer (CDT). With a full service state of the art machining center and a full service manufacturing facility along with an experienced and dedicated engineering group there is no project we couldnt handle.
Control Products Corporation remains an innovative leader in the aerospace lighting industry, exceeding rigorous standards for Night Vision Imaging Systems and flight simulator solutions for rotary and fixed-wing aircraft around the world.  When you need a partner with unmatched experienced; a partner with a rich history of providing quality workmanship while exceeding the expectations of their clients, look no further than Control Products Corporation – The World leader in aircraft lighting systems and flight simulators.










